headline: Enbridge (ENB) Beats Q2 Earnings and Revenue Estimates
summary: Enbridge (ENB) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of +14.63% and +18.08%, respectively, for the quarter ended June 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
